{"componentChunkName":"component---node-modules-carrotsearch-gatsby-theme-apidocs-templates-documentation-page-js","path":"/","result":{"data":{"html":{"frontmatter":{"id":"hello-carrot2","title":"Hello, Carrot2!"},"html":"<article>\n  <h1>Hello, Carrot<sup>2</sup>!</h1>\n\n  <p id=\"0317a56a6eab4596bf8e40a7\">\n    Carrot<sup>2</sup> is a programming library for clustering text. It can automatically discover groups of\n    related documents and label them with short key terms or phrases.\n  </p>\n\n  <p id=\"cb3eda7b90249de238a70172\">\n    Carrot<sup>2</sup> can, for example, organize search results into groups like these:\n  </p>\n\n  <figure class=\"round\">\n    <div style=\"position: relative\">\n        <span style=\"padding-bottom: 52.77777777777778%; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,')\" class=\"preview light fluid\"> </span>\n        <img class=\"light fluid\" alt=\"Search results (snippets) and clusters discovered from them, light theme.\" title src=\"../static/146062e8a96c2e1f519278c40365c57c/37523/carrot2-intro-example-light.png\" srcset=\"../static/146062e8a96c2e1f519278c40365c57c/e9ff0/carrot2-intro-example-light.png 180w,\n../static/146062e8a96c2e1f519278c40365c57c/f21e7/carrot2-intro-example-light.png 360w,\n../static/146062e8a96c2e1f519278c40365c57c/37523/carrot2-intro-example-light.png 720w,\n../static/146062e8a96c2e1f519278c40365c57c/302a4/carrot2-intro-example-light.png 1080w,\n../static/146062e8a96c2e1f519278c40365c57c/07a9c/carrot2-intro-example-light.png 1440w,\n../static/146062e8a96c2e1f519278c40365c57c/966c1/carrot2-intro-example-light.png 1694w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\">\n      </div>\n    <div style=\"position: relative\">\n        <span style=\"padding-bottom: 52.77777777777778%; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,')\" class=\"preview dark fluid\"> </span>\n        <img class=\"dark fluid\" alt=\"Search results (snippets) and clusters discovered from them, dark theme.\" title src=\"../static/885ae93354abfed96bd0c3b417bfe9b9/37523/carrot2-intro-example-dark.png\" srcset=\"../static/885ae93354abfed96bd0c3b417bfe9b9/e9ff0/carrot2-intro-example-dark.png 180w,\n../static/885ae93354abfed96bd0c3b417bfe9b9/f21e7/carrot2-intro-example-dark.png 360w,\n../static/885ae93354abfed96bd0c3b417bfe9b9/37523/carrot2-intro-example-dark.png 720w,\n../static/885ae93354abfed96bd0c3b417bfe9b9/302a4/carrot2-intro-example-dark.png 1080w,\n../static/885ae93354abfed96bd0c3b417bfe9b9/07a9c/carrot2-intro-example-dark.png 1440w,\n../static/885ae93354abfed96bd0c3b417bfe9b9/966c1/carrot2-intro-example-dark.png 1694w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\">\n      </div>\n    <figcaption>\n      <p>\n        Search result titles and snippets (on the left) for query \"salsa\"\n        and corresponding cluster labels (right).\n      </p>\n    </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n\n  <section id=\"what-is-in-the-box\">\n    <h2>\n        <a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#what-is-in-the-box\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"/></svg></a>What's in the box\n      </h2>\n\n    <p id=\"caa7da6570f2d3bf7653eefa\">\n      Carrot<sup>2</sup> provides a common infrastructure and a number of algorithms for\n      <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cluster_analysis\">clustering</a> of text.\n      Out-of-the-box, Carrot<sup>2</sup> distribution comes with:\n    </p>\n\n    <ul>\n      <li id=\"40601fd9fa047a30bc752a49\">the <a href=\"/java-api-basics/\">Java API</a> and\n        several <a href=\"/choosing-clustering-algorithm/\">clustering algorithm implementations</a>,</li>\n      <li id=\"0ac2cb019a73b85b0c22fb55\">the <a href=\"/rest-api-basics/\">REST service</a>\n        for mash-ups or integration with languages other than Java,</li>\n      <li id=\"49cfee2a344808c4051acfc0\">the <a href=\"https://search.carrot2.org\" target=\"_blank\">Search Results Clustering</a> demo application,</li>\n      <li id=\"22c7fa7f1fd9c79e1cac4272\">the <a href=\"https://search.carrot2.org/#/workbench\" target=\"_blank\">Clustering Workbench</a> application\n        for more advanced users,</li>\n      <li id=\"00c6f0f4cee739d873bc3fc2\">code snippets and examples for reuse in your code.</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <p id=\"141c67d82ca195bd1b1c8e58\">\n      Additionally, several downstream projects provide integration between Carrot<sup>2</sup>\n      and popular document retrieval services:\n    </p>\n\n    <ul>\n      <li id=\"4d601dd9a700cbda4405bb7f\"><a href=\"https://lucene.apache.org/solr/\">Apache Solr</a> has\n        <a href=\"https://lucene.apache.org/solr/guide/8_2/result-clustering.html\">built-in\n          support</a> for clustering search results via Carrot<sup>2</sup> algorithms,\n      </li>\n      <li id=\"9b342cb8438e1033c7dc2223\"><a href=\"https://github.com/carrot2/elasticsearch-carrot2\">elasticsearch-carrot2</a>\n        plugin provides search results clustering for\n        <a href=\"https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch\">Elasticsearch</a>.</li>\n    </ul>\n  </section>\n</article>","tableOfContents":[{"heading":"What's in the box","anchor":"what-is-in-the-box"}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/hello-carrot2/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1164750013"]}